=== CARGO_GRAVEYARD ===
# id: 84
# title: The Cargo Graveyard
# chinese_title: 货物坟场
# category: Wreckage
# mode: dungeon

Hundreds of cargo containers float in a tangled mass, the remains of a convoy ambush. Many are breached, their contents scattered to the void. A few sealed containers drift among the wreckage, their manifests unreadable beneath blast scoring.

* [Crack open a sealed container]
  ~ gain_gold(35)
  "货" (huò) — goods, cargo
* [Scan for containers with valuable contents]
  ~ gain_item("credit_chip")
  "搜" (sōu) — to search, to scan
* [Look for survivors or escape pods]
  ~ gain_radical("人")
  "活" (huó) — alive, living, to survive
* [Salvage hull plating for repairs]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "废" (fèi) — waste, scrap, abandoned
